Edited November 26, 2014 by tetryds

The following snippet suggests that you have run out of memory:

Error occurred at 2014-11-26_122032.
C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Kerbal Space Program\KSP.exe, run by donovan.
71% memory in use.
0 MB physical memory [2277 MB free].
0 MB paging file [0 MB free].
0 MB user address space [63 MB free].
Write to location 0000000c caused an access violation.

Assuming you haven't installed any add-ons/mods, your only option is to upgrade your computer's RAM (2GB RAM is dangerously insufficient - you need at least 4GB RAM to run KSP 0.25).
I finally got it to work. It just needed to be re-installed and the mods reapplied. Thank you for your timely response.
